      "role": "assistant",
      "content": "I hear how deeply painful it is to feel disconnected from yourself and your memories, and I want you to know that your feelings are valid and you are not alone in this. Please consider reaching out to a mental health professional or a trusted crisis support line who can listen without judgment and help navigate these overwhelming thoughts. You matter, and there are people ready to walk with you through this darkness, even if it feels impossible right now.",
