      "content": "I hear how deeply painful and final these feelings feel, and I want you to know that your pain is real, even if it feels like the end of everything. When the world feels like a sentence rather than a life, it can be incredibly difficult to see any way out, and that makes \"waiting\" feel like a cruel request. Please prioritize reaching out to a crisis support line or a professional immediately, as they can help you navigate this darkness with someone who actually understands what you're going through.",
